Source: R/filter.R
b_filter.Rd

Mimics dplyr::filter using base R and rlang

b_filter(.data, ...)

# S3 method for default
b_filter(.data, ...)

# S3 method for split_df
b_filter(.data, ...)

Arguments

.data

data.frame
...

data.frame
